---
layout: layouts/base.njk
permalink: /books/
title: Books
---

<div class="index-page">
  <h1>The Volumes</h1>
  <p class="index-page__lede">
    The archive consists of two scrapbook volumes compiled by family members
    over the course of the late nineteenth and twentieth centuries. Each
    contains scanned pages with full transcriptions where the handwriting has
    been deciphered.
  </p>

  <div class="home-books">
    {%- for book, pages in collections.pagesByBook -%}
      <a href="/books/book-{{ book | padPage }}/" class="home-book">
        <div class="home-book__num">{{ books[book].label }}</div>
        <h3 class="home-book__title">{{ books[book].title }}</h3>
        <p class="home-book__count">{{ pages.length }} {{ books[book].unit }}{% if pages.length != 1 %}s{% endif %} transcribed</p>
      </a>
    {%- endfor -%}
  </div>
</div>
